T1  - On the presence and market-structure of exchanges around the world
AU  - Clayton, Matthew J.
AU  - Jorgensen, Bjorn N.
AU  - Kavajecz, Kenneth A.
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 9
IS  - 1
SP  - 27
EP  - 48
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/02/01/
